{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Well, this is about state budgets."},{"time":2000,"text":"This is probably the most boring topic"},{"time":5000,"text":"of the whole morning."},{"time":7000,"text":"But I want to tell you, I think it's an important topic"},{"time":10000,"text":"that we need to care about."},{"time":13000,"text":"State budgets"},{"time":15000,"text":"are big, big money --"},{"time":18000,"text":"I'll show you the numbers --"},{"time":20000,"text":"and they get very little scrutiny."},{"time":23000,"text":"The understanding is very low."},{"time":26000,"text":"Many of the people involved"},{"time":28000,"text":"have special interests or short-term interests"},{"time":30000,"text":"that get them not thinking"},{"time":32000,"text":"about what the implications of the trends are."},{"time":36000,"text":"And these budgets"},{"time":38000,"text":"are the key for our future;"},{"time":40000,"text":"they're the key for our kids."},{"time":42000,"text":"Most education funding --"},{"time":44000,"text":"whether it's K through 12,"},{"time":46000,"text":"or the great universities or community colleges --"},{"time":49000,"text":"most of the money for those things"},{"time":51000,"text":"is coming out of these state budgets."}]},{"cues":[{"time":54000,"text":"But we have a problem."},{"time":56000,"text":"Here's the overall picture."},{"time":58000,"text":"U.S. economy is big --"},{"time":61000,"text":"14.7 trillion."},{"time":63000,"text":"Now out of that pie,"},{"time":65000,"text":"the government spends 36 percent."},{"time":68000,"text":"So this is combining the federal level,"},{"time":70000,"text":"which is the largest,"},{"time":72000,"text":"the state level and the local level."},{"time":74000,"text":"And it's really in this combined way"},{"time":76000,"text":"that you get an overall sense of what's going on,"},{"time":78000,"text":"because there's a lot of complex things"},{"time":80000,"text":"like Medicaid and research money"},{"time":82000,"text":"that flow across those boundaries."},{"time":85000,"text":"But we're spending 36 percent."},{"time":87000,"text":"Well what are we taking in?"},{"time":89000,"text":"Simple business question."},{"time":91000,"text":"Answer is 26 percent."},{"time":95000,"text":"Now this leaves 10 percent deficit,"},{"time":100000,"text":"sort of a mind-blowing number."},{"time":103000,"text":"And some of that, in fact, is due to the fact"},{"time":106000,"text":"that we've had an economic recession."},{"time":108000,"text":"Receipts go down,"},{"time":110000,"text":"some spending programs go up,"},{"time":112000,"text":"but most of it is not because of that."},{"time":115000,"text":"Most of it is because of ways"},{"time":117000,"text":"that the liabilities are building up"},{"time":119000,"text":"and the trends,"},{"time":121000,"text":"and that creates a huge challenge."},{"time":124000,"text":"In fact, this is the forecast picture."},{"time":127000,"text":"There are various things in here:"},{"time":129000,"text":"I could say we might raise more revenue,"},{"time":131000,"text":"or medical innovation will make the spending even higher."},{"time":135000,"text":"It is an increasingly difficult picture,"},{"time":138000,"text":"even assuming the economy does quite well --"},{"time":141000,"text":"probably better than it will do."},{"time":144000,"text":"This is what you see"},{"time":146000,"text":"at this overall level."}]},{"cues":[{"time":148000,"text":"Now how did we get here?"},{"time":150000,"text":"How could you have a problem like this?"},{"time":153000,"text":"After all, at least on paper,"},{"time":156000,"text":"there's this notion that these state budgets are balanced."},{"time":159000,"text":"Only one state says"},{"time":161000,"text":"they don't have to balance the budget."},{"time":163000,"text":"But what this means actually"},{"time":165000,"text":"is that there's a pretense."},{"time":167000,"text":"There's no real, true balancing going on,"},{"time":170000,"text":"and in a sense, the games they play to hide that"},{"time":174000,"text":"actually obscure the topic so much"},{"time":176000,"text":"that people don't see things"},{"time":178000,"text":"that are actually pretty straight-forward challenges."},{"time":182000,"text":"When Jerry Brown was elected,"},{"time":184000,"text":"this was the challenge that was put to him."},{"time":186000,"text":"That is, through various gimmicks and things,"},{"time":189000,"text":"a so-called balanced budget"},{"time":192000,"text":"had led him to have 25 billion missing"},{"time":196000,"text":"out of the 76 billion in proposed spending."},{"time":199000,"text":"Now he's put together some thoughts:"},{"time":201000,"text":"About half of that he'll cut,"},{"time":204000,"text":"another half,"},{"time":206000,"text":"perhaps in a very complex set of steps,"},{"time":208000,"text":"taxes will be approved."},{"time":210000,"text":"But even so,"},{"time":212000,"text":"as you go out into those future years,"},{"time":215000,"text":"various pension costs, health costs go up enough,"},{"time":218000,"text":"and the revenue does not go up enough."},{"time":221000,"text":"So you get a big squeeze."}]},{"cues":[{"time":223000,"text":"What were those things that allowed us to hide this?"},{"time":226000,"text":"Well, some really nice little tricks."},{"time":229000,"text":"And these were somewhat noticed."},{"time":231000,"text":"The paper said, \"It's not really balanced."},{"time":233000,"text":"It's got holes."},{"time":235000,"text":"It perpetuates deficit spending."},{"time":237000,"text":"It's riddled with gimmicks.\""},{"time":240000,"text":"And really when you get down to it,"},{"time":243000,"text":"the guys at Enron never would have done this."},{"time":246000,"text":"This is so blatant,"},{"time":248000,"text":"so extreme."},{"time":251000,"text":"Is anyone paying attention"},{"time":253000,"text":"to some of the things these guys do?"},{"time":256000,"text":"They borrow money."},{"time":258000,"text":"They're not supposed to, but they figure out a way."},{"time":260000,"text":"They make you pay more in withholding"},{"time":262000,"text":"just to help their cash flow out."},{"time":264000,"text":"They sell off the assets."},{"time":266000,"text":"They defer the payments."},{"time":269000,"text":"They sell off the revenues from tobacco."},{"time":271000,"text":"And California's not unique."},{"time":273000,"text":"In fact, there's about five states that are worse"},{"time":275000,"text":"and only really four states"},{"time":277000,"text":"that don't face this big challenge."},{"time":279000,"text":"So it's systemic across the entire country."},{"time":282000,"text":"It really comes from the fact"},{"time":284000,"text":"that certain long-term obligations --"},{"time":286000,"text":"health care, where innovation makes it more expensive,"},{"time":289000,"text":"early retirement and pension, where the age structure gets worse for you,"},{"time":292000,"text":"and just generosity --"},{"time":294000,"text":"that these mis-accounting things"},{"time":296000,"text":"allow to develop over time,"},{"time":298000,"text":"that you've got a problem."},{"time":301000,"text":"This is the retiree health care benefits."},{"time":303000,"text":"Three million set aside, 62 billion dollar liability --"},{"time":306000,"text":"much worse than the car companies."},{"time":308000,"text":"And everybody looked at that"},{"time":310000,"text":"and knew that that was headed toward a huge problem."},{"time":313000,"text":"The forecast for the medical piece alone"},{"time":315000,"text":"is to go from 26 percent of the budget"},{"time":317000,"text":"to 42 percent."}]},{"cues":[{"time":319000,"text":"Well what's going to give?"},{"time":321000,"text":"Well in order to accommodate that,"},{"time":323000,"text":"you would have to cut education spending in half."},{"time":327000,"text":"It really is this young versus the old"},{"time":329000,"text":"to some degree."},{"time":331000,"text":"If you don't change that revenue picture,"},{"time":334000,"text":"if you don't solve what you're doing in health care,"},{"time":336000,"text":"you're going to be deinvesting in the young."},{"time":339000,"text":"The great University of California university system,"},{"time":342000,"text":"the great things that have gone on,"},{"time":344000,"text":"won't happen."},{"time":346000,"text":"So far it's meant layoffs,"},{"time":348000,"text":"increased class sizes."},{"time":350000,"text":"Within the education community there's this discussion of,"},{"time":353000,"text":"\"Should it just be the young teachers who get laid off,"},{"time":355000,"text":"or the less good teachers who get laid off?\""},{"time":357000,"text":"And there's a discussion: if you're going to increase class sizes,"},{"time":360000,"text":"where do you do that? How much effect does that have?"},{"time":363000,"text":"And unfortunately, as you get into that, people get confused and think,"},{"time":366000,"text":"well maybe you think that's okay."},{"time":368000,"text":"In fact, no, education spending should not be cut."},{"time":371000,"text":"There's ways, if it's temporary,"},{"time":373000,"text":"to minimize the impact,"},{"time":375000,"text":"but it's a problem."},{"time":377000,"text":"It's also really a problem for where we need to go."},{"time":379000,"text":"Technology has a role to play."},{"time":381000,"text":"Well we need money to experiment with that,"},{"time":384000,"text":"to get those tools in there."},{"time":386000,"text":"There's the idea of paying teachers for effectiveness,"},{"time":388000,"text":"measuring them, giving them feedback,"},{"time":390000,"text":"taking videos in the classroom."},{"time":392000,"text":"That's something I think is very, very important."},{"time":394000,"text":"Well you have to allocate dollars"},{"time":396000,"text":"for that system"},{"time":398000,"text":"and for that incentive pay."},{"time":400000,"text":"In a situation where you have growth,"},{"time":402000,"text":"you put the new money into this."},{"time":404000,"text":"Or even if you're flat, you might shift money into it."},{"time":406000,"text":"But with the type of cuts we're talking about,"},{"time":408000,"text":"it will be far, far harder"},{"time":410000,"text":"to get these incentives for excellence,"},{"time":412000,"text":"or to move over"},{"time":414000,"text":"to use technology in the new way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":417000,"text":"So what's going on?"},{"time":419000,"text":"Where's the brain trust"},{"time":421000,"text":"that's in error here?"},{"time":423000,"text":"Well there really is no brain trust."},{"time":426000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":428000,"text":"It's sort of the voters. It's sort of us showing up."},{"time":432000,"text":"Just look at this spending."},{"time":434000,"text":"California will spend over 100 billion,"},{"time":436000,"text":"Microsoft, 38,"},{"time":438000,"text":"Google, about 19."},{"time":440000,"text":"The amount of IQ in good numeric analysis,"},{"time":443000,"text":"both inside Google and Microsoft"},{"time":445000,"text":"and outside, with analysts and people of various opinions --"},{"time":448000,"text":"should they have spent on that?"},{"time":450000,"text":"No, they wasted their money on this. What about this thing? --"},{"time":452000,"text":"it really is quite phenomenal."},{"time":455000,"text":"Everybody has an opinion."},{"time":457000,"text":"There's great feedback."},{"time":460000,"text":"And the numbers are used to make decisions."},{"time":463000,"text":"If you go over the education spending and the health care spending --"},{"time":466000,"text":"particularly these long-term trends --"},{"time":469000,"text":"you don't have that type of involvement"},{"time":471000,"text":"on a number that's more important"},{"time":473000,"text":"in terms of equity, in terms of learning."}]},{"cues":[{"time":476000,"text":"So what do we need to do?"},{"time":478000,"text":"We need better tools."},{"time":480000,"text":"We can get some things out on the Internet."},{"time":482000,"text":"I'm going to use my website"},{"time":484000,"text":"to put up some things that will give the basic picture."},{"time":486000,"text":"We need lots more."},{"time":488000,"text":"There's a few good books,"},{"time":490000,"text":"one about school spending and where the money comes from --"},{"time":492000,"text":"how that's changed over time, and the challenge."},{"time":495000,"text":"We need better accounting."},{"time":497000,"text":"We need to take the fact"},{"time":499000,"text":"that the current employees, the future liabilities they create,"},{"time":501000,"text":"that should come out of the current budget."},{"time":504000,"text":"We need to understand why they've done the pension accounting"},{"time":506000,"text":"the way they have."},{"time":508000,"text":"It should be more like private accounting."},{"time":510000,"text":"It's the gold standard."},{"time":512000,"text":"And finally, we need to really reward politicians."},{"time":515000,"text":"Whenever they say there's these long-term problems,"},{"time":517000,"text":"we can't say, \"Oh, you're the messenger with bad news?"},{"time":519000,"text":"We just shot you.\""},{"time":522000,"text":"In fact, there are some like these:"},{"time":524000,"text":"Erskine Bowles, Alan Simpson and others,"},{"time":526000,"text":"who have gone through and given proposals"},{"time":529000,"text":"for this overall federal health-spending state-level problem."},{"time":533000,"text":"But in fact, their work was sort of pushed off."},{"time":535000,"text":"In fact, the week afterwards,"},{"time":538000,"text":"some tax cuts were done"},{"time":540000,"text":"that made the situation even worse"},{"time":542000,"text":"than their assumptions."},{"time":544000,"text":"So we need these pieces."}]},{"cues":[{"time":546000,"text":"Now I think this is a solvable problem."},{"time":549000,"text":"It's a great country with lots of people."},{"time":552000,"text":"But we have to draw those people in,"},{"time":556000,"text":"because this is about education."},{"time":558000,"text":"And just look at what happened with the tuitions"},{"time":560000,"text":"with the University of California"},{"time":562000,"text":"and project that out for another three, four, five years --"},{"time":565000,"text":"it's unaffordable."},{"time":568000,"text":"And that's the kind of thing --"},{"time":570000,"text":"the investment in the young --"},{"time":572000,"text":"that makes us great, allows us to contribute."},{"time":574000,"text":"It allows us to do the art,"},{"time":576000,"text":"the biotechnology, the software"},{"time":579000,"text":"and all those magic things."},{"time":582000,"text":"And so the bottom line is"},{"time":584000,"text":"we need to care about state budgets"},{"time":587000,"text":"because they're critical for our kids and our future."}]},{"cues":[{"time":589000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":591000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}